WEBVTT

00:00:00.785 --> 00:00:03.840
Njiani kufika hapa,

00:00:03.840 --> 00:00:07.542
nilikuwa na mazungumzo mazuri na 
mtu aliyekuwa anakaa pembeni yangu kwenye

00:00:07.542 --> 00:00:10.562
ndege. Alinambia 


00:00:10.562 --> 00:00:13.805
"Hamna kazi tena USA,

00:00:13.805 --> 00:00:16.073
yaani sasa wamebuni kazi mpya:

00:00:16.083 --> 00:00:21.373
mwanasaikolojia wa paka,
mzungumzaji wa mbwa,msasi wa kimbunga."

00:00:21.373 --> 00:00:24.453
Punde, aliniuliza,

00:00:24.453 --> 00:00:27.132
"Kwani wewe unafanya kazi gani?"

00:00:27.132 --> 00:00:29.722
Nikamjibu, "Mjenzi wa usalama?"

00:00:29.722 --> 00:00:33.025
(Vicheko)